title: Hour 3 - NFL Camps, Ross Tucker
itunes:title: Hour 3 - NFL Camps, Ross Tucker
description:
Dan takes a look at the relevant stories coming out of NFL training camps, and former NFL OL, Ross Tucker stops by to talk about his experience at the NFL Hall of Fame induction ceremony over the weekend.
